# Building the project:
Just run `make run` to build and run.

# Features
* real-time GPU cloth simulation
* gravity and wind affect the cloth
* the user-controllable ball allows interaction with the cloth

# Controls
* move mouse to move ball
* click and drag to rotate orbital camera
* press W and S to zoom in and out
* press 1 to toggle wireframe rendering
* press 2 to toggle specular highlights
* press F to toggle freezing the ball in place

